reviewText: The documentary approach of this film raises the credibility factor of WHO IS DELSIN? to a special level. There are some very "real" characters in this film that weave a shocking tale of reality versus mythology. You will not easily forget WHO IS DELSIN?

I HAD THE PLEASURE OF SEEING A PREVIEW OF DELSIN AFTER IT WAS COMPLETED. IT IS A THRILLER FILLED WITH SUSPENSE AND A CLEVER PLOT. IF YOU LIKE ACTION FILMS FILLED WITH SUSPENSE AND AT THE SAME MAKES YOU THINK, THIS IS YOUR FILM. IT BORDERS ON FICTION AND REALITY AND LEAVES YOU WONDERING IF IT IT COULD REALLY BE TRUE.
